On our path of #discoveringnovelty, we at Mercadeo have raised the bar higher! 🔝
Taking on to next level of marketing, for the first time ever in the DU circuit a society’s annual event was promoted at Ambience mall (Vasant Kunj and Gurgaon) and the moment was worth cherishing forever.

So, buckle up and register fast for the ultimate marketing extravaganza of the year, INCENDO: Esprit De Corps 🔥

Registration link in bio!

👑Our vision is set on the future, we can do everything but can never forget about our humble past!
⚡Every meeting, every moment & celebration all trickles down to this beautiful journey 🥂
Not to miss "Many more to come"💖

latestPosts.caption:
Do you ever get tired of pretending to be okay and faking that smile, when you're barely holding it together on the inside? 🫠

The first step to healing is asking for help and Reawakening Wellness Foundation is just the place for that! Providing emotional counselling, rehabilitation, and mental wellness care, helping people reclaim their lives because no one should have to carry it all alone 🫂

Behind every smile, there could be a storm, and it deserves real support 🫶🏻

Now that the cheers of the crowd have settled, it's starting to sink in that we've walked through a decade of passion, growth, and excellence 💥

What started as just another date on the calendar has turned into an unforgettable memory. The crowd, the panel, the participants, everyone brought in something unique and it was the perfect collision of eager minds and enthusiastic voices 🍃

Here's to the bonds built, the highs and the lows, and the promise of coming back together more inspired than ever 🪄

latestPosts.caption:
It's a joy to finally unveil the sponsors of INCENDO 10.0! 🥳
A big cheer to our sponsors who helped shape our event into something much bigger than we ever imagined 💫

Hamari Bagiya crafts pots, planters and flowers for plant lovers that can brighter any corner of your home and turn them into peaceful sanctuaries. 

Rage Room is place where you can scream, smash and break things to fix your peace and leave with a lighter heart.

Evnoi is a brand that turns ordinary stationery items into pretty tools for thinkers, dreamers and believers whose ideas deserve to rest on beautiful pages. 

XTCY is a non-alcoholic energy drink brand specially curated for late-night workers, risk-takers and all those who need the focus of a freshly charged brain. 

Interview Buddy is the mentor you didn't know you needed to help you face interviews with fierce readiness and confidence. 

Lisse stitch is a company focused on fashion that's both trendy and practical for student life.

Lazer Crazer is one of the finest gaming lounges in Delhi NCR that offers a wide selection of laser tag action, racing simulators, VR gaming, and gel paintball.

BlissBuns a brand that designs beautiful, minimalist jewelry and focuses on affordable accessories for everyday elegance. 

The magic of INCENDO'25 was fueled by the brilliance, unwavering support and strength of our amazing sponsors 🪄

latestPosts.caption:
Unmasking the brilliant voices that'll take the mic at INCENDO'25!

Introducing Simar Sekhri, the visionary Co-founder of Hive School, India's first B-School dedicated to marketing and sales where students sharpen their skills in leadership, strategy and growth💡

From appearing on Shark Tank S4 to mentoring the next generation of business leaders, Simar's journey is a masterclass in redefining education and empowering others to make real life impact in the field of marketing 🎯

Gear up for an inspiring speaker session as Simar joins us in INCENDO 10.0 and shares his real-world insights, preparing future business leaders to truly dominate the marketing space like no one else 🚀
